10) Example endpoint → Action mappings (illustrative)

Site (Editor/Admin):
	•	PUT /tenants/{tenantId}/site/home → SITE_EDIT
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/site/publish → SITE_PUBLISH (admin only)

Store (Staff/Admin, requires CAP_STORE):
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/products → PRODUCT_MANAGE
	•	PUT /tenants/{tenantId}/products/{id} → PRODUCT_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/products/{id}/images → PRODUCT_MEDIA_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/categories → CATEGORY_MANAGE

Orders/Selling (Staff/Admin, requires CAP_STORE):
	•	GET /tenants/{tenantId}/orders → ORDER_VIEW
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/orders/{orderId}/status → ORDER_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/orders/{orderId}/refund → REFUND_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/sales → SALE_CREATE

Scheduling (Staff/Admin, requires CAP_SCHEDULING):
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/services → SERVICE_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/bookings → BOOKING_MANAGE

Admin Settings (Admin only):
	•	PUT /tenants/{tenantId}/payments/wompi → PAYMENT_SETTINGS_MANAGE
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/staff/invite → STAFF_MANAGE
	•	PUT /tenants/{tenantId}/domains/{domainId} → DOMAIN_MANAGE

