11) Audit requirements (recommended baseline)

For sensitive actions, write audit logs (tenantId/userId/role):
	•	PAYMENT_SETTINGS_MANAGE
	•	DOMAIN_MANAGE
	•	STAFF_MANAGE
	•	SITE_PUBLISH
	•	REFUND_MANAGE
	•	Order status changes (ORDER_MANAGE)

This helps support and reduces fraud risk.

⸻

12) Final locked decisions summary
	•	Centralized policy (Option B) is the sole authorization source
	•	Roles: ADMIN (all), STAFF (ops + refunds + pricing), EDITOR (site edit only)
	•	Publish: ADMIN only
	•	Payment settings: ADMIN only
	•	Capabilities gate modules by plan (store/scheduling)
	•	Multi-tenant memberships allowed; token scoped to one tenant
	•	Membership disabled → immediate access loss
	•	Refresh rotation enabled; reuse triggers family revoke

